  <refsect1 id="description-gtktextview">
    <title>Description</title>

      <para>
        A <link linkend="class-gtksourceview2"><classname>gtksourceview2.View</classname></link>
        is a text widget that extends the standard <link linkend="class-gtktextview"><classname>gtk.TextView</classname></link>
        It improves the <link linkend="class-gtktextview"><classname>gtk.TextView</classname></link> by implementing syntax highlighting
        and other features typical of a source editor.</para>
  </refsect1>

